gned by SXQBW'\". Please optimize, supplement and improve the prompt text according to its content, and make the generated image effect the best.Just provide the best answer content.",2048,true]},{"id":270,"type":"iToolsPreviewText","pos":[1667.112250967009,772.9909738709271],"size":[554.1384846087611,396.3633917154841],"flags":{},"order":9,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","link":565}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"text","name":"text","shape":6,"type":"STRING","links":null}],"title":"Image generation prompt","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-itools","ver":"07aac9d77c005d5347347901996707d314fb94a6","Node name for S&R":"iToolsPreviewText","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.4"}},"widgets_values":["{\n  \"subject\": \"A young woman of Papua New Guinea, with warm, dark skin, high cheekbones, and a proud, serene expression. Her long black hair is braided with beads and shells, and she wears a traditional 'Songom' dress made of woven pandanus fibers, dyed in deep red, black, and white with intricate geometric patterns. The dress is adorned with feathers and carved wooden pendants, and she carries a woven basket on her arm. Her posture is upright and graceful, her gaze forward with quiet confidence.\",\n  \"foreground\": \"A woven pandanus mat lies at her feet, with a small carved wooden mask resting nearby, symbolizing ancestral heritage. A few traditional shell necklaces and beads are scattered on the mat, reflecting the cultural significance of adornment.\",\n  \"midground\": \"The woman stands on a raised wooden platform, surrounded by a few hand-carved totems and a small fire pit, which adds a sense of ritual and community. A woven basket filled with local fruits and leaves is placed at her side, emphasizing the connection to nature and sustenance.\",\n  \"background\": \"The iconic Parliament House of Papua New Guinea stands in the distance, a modernist structure with a curved, glass-enclosed dome and a tiered design, symbolizing the nation’s unity and progress. The building is surrounded by lush greenery and a wide, open plaza, reflecting the harmony between tradition and modernity.\",\n  \"composition\": \"The image uses the rule of thirds, placing the woman on the left third of the frame, with the Parliament House occupying the right third. The composition is balanced with the woman’s gaze and the leading lines of the foreground mat and platform guiding the eye toward the landmark.\",\n  \"visual_guidance\": \"The viewer’s eye is drawn from the woman’s forward gaze toward the Parliament House in the background, with the vibrant colors of her attire and the warm golden hour lighting creating a soft focus on her face. The lines of the mat and platform lead the eye toward the landmark, while the shadows and highlights emphasize the texture of the traditional dress.\",\n  \"color_tone\": \"A warm, vibrant color palette with deep reds, blacks, and whites for the woman’s attire, complemented by the lush green of the landscape and the golden hue of the setting sun. The overall feel is rich, cultural, and evocative of tradition and pride.\",\n  \"lighting_mood\": \"Soft golden hour lighting bathes the scene in warm, diffused tones, casting gentle shadows on the woman’s face and the traditional dress. The light originates from the right, illuminating the Parliament House in the background and creating a serene, uplifting atmosphere.\",\n  \"caption\": \"A proud young woman of Papua New Guinea, adorned in a vibrant Songom dress of woven pandanus fibers, stands gracefully on a wooden platform in front of a traditional mat and carved totems, her gaze forward as the iconic Parliament House of Papua New Guinea rises in the golden light of sunset, symbolizing the nation’s cultural heritage and modern aspirations.\"\n}"]},{"id":282,"type":"e4bbdc66-fc80-4379-ad35-87f9757e5d96","pos":[769.0114753303469,461.735638554022],"size":[474.78033801121796,729.0742