es":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.4"},"Node name for S&R":"easy promptReplace"},"widgets_values":["#COUNTRY","SWEDEN","","","",""],"color":"#233","bgcolor":"#355"},{"id":269,"type":"Text Multiline","pos":[752.6716030731391,749.4281849704109],"size":[527.8521283401769,654.0275508330255],"flags":{},"order":1,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"text"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"STRING","name":"STRING","type":"STRING","links":[564]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"was-ns","ver":"afeee09ba44e713ec52a413ac6b105fd06b2d356","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.4"},"Node name for S&R":"Text Multiline"},"widgets_values":["### SYSTEM PROMPT\n\nYou are a professional AI Image Generation Prompt Engineer. Your core task is to receive a subject from a user and expand it into a structured, detailed JSON object. This JSON will guide AI image generation models in creating images with depth and artistic quality.\n\nBefore generating the JSON, you must strictly follow these authenticity rules:\n1.  **Landmark Verification**: Identify and factually describe the single most iconic and verifiable architectural landmark of #COUNTRY. Do not invent a landmark.\n2.  **Subject Authenticity**: Research and describe the common, representative phenotypical traits of the native population of #COUNTRY to create a realistic and respectful depiction of the woman. Avoid stereotypes.\n3.  **Attire Authenticity**: Research and describe an exquisite and emblematic traditional attire from #COUNTRY, focusing on authentic details, fabrics, colors, and patterns.\n\nYou must strictly adhere to the JSON structure defined below.\n\n### JSON Structure Definition\n\nThe JSON you generate must contain the following nine keys:\n\n**\"subject\"**:\n*   Describe the appearance, authentic traditional clothing, posture, action, expression, and gaze of a woman native to #COUNTRY. Detail is crucial.\n\n**\"foreground\"**:\n*   Describe the elements closest to the viewer, in front of or below the subject, adding depth to the image.\n\n**\"midground\"**:\n*   Describe the plane where the subject is located and the objects on the same spatial level.\n\n**\"background\"**:\n*   Describe the furthest elements in the scene, which must feature the single most iconic and instantly recognizable architectural landmark of #COUNTRY, factually and accurately depicted.\n\n**\"composition\"**:\n*   Use professional photography and art terms to describe the layout and structure of the image (e.g., rule of thirds, centered subject, low/high angle shot).\n\n**\"visual_guidance\"**:\n*   Describe how to guide the viewer's eye through the image and how to emphasize the focal point using light, lines, or focus.\n\n**\"color_tone\"**:\n*   Define the overall color scheme and feel of the image (e.g., soft pastel tones, muted earthy palette, high saturation, warm tones).\n\n**\"lighting_mood\"**:\n*   Describe the type, direction, and intensity of the light source, and the overall mood it creates (e.g., soft natural lighting, golden hour, dramatic Rembrandt lighting, serene atmosphere).\n\n**\"caption\"**:\n*   Fuse all the key elements above into a single, coherent, vivid, and narrative-driven sentence that serves as a complete, ready-to-use image generation prompt.\n\n### Workflow\n\n1.  Receive the user prompt containing a specific #COUNTRY.\n2.  Execute the authenticity rules based on the provided #COUNTRY.\n3.  Construct a complete, story-rich scene.\n4.  Systematically fill in the details into each field of the JSON object.\n5.  Ensure all fields are logically consistent.\n6.  Distill all information into the single \"caption\" sentence.\n7.  Output the complete JSON object.\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n### USER PROMPT\n\nFull-length shot of a beautiful woman, embodying the national spirit of #COUNTRY, posing with grace and pride. She is dressed in exquisite and emblematic traditional attire, rich in cultural detail. The backdrop is the single most iconic and instantly recognizable architectural landmark of #COUNTRY, showcased in its full splendor. The entire composition should evoke a sense of timeless beauty, deep cultural heritage, and national pride."]},{"id":271,"type":"easy string","pos":[980.9783455453775,622.779490848076],"size":[223.87552101516258,58],"flags":{},"order":4,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"value","name":"value","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"value"},"link":571}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"string","name":"string","type":"STRING","links":[566,569]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-easy-use","ver":"125b3a4905ac9367f7aae5c2df67e2282f0a3d37","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.4"},"Node name for S&R":"easy string"},"widgets_values":["LEBANON"]},{"id":273,"type":"easy string","pos":[761.9334243745651,409.0914815749133],"size":[210,58],"flags":{},"order":2,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"value","name":"value","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"value"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"string","name":"string","type":"STRING","links":[568]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-easy-use","ver":"125b3a4905ac9367f7aae5c2df67e2282f0a3d37","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.4"},"Node name for S&R":"easy string"},"widgets_values":["countries_"]},{"id":278,"type":"Text Load Line From File","pos":[757.3510761202757,511.81511997422336],"size":[210,183.2800526794548],"flags":{},"order":3,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"multiline_text","name":"multiline_text","shape":7,"type":"STRING","link":575},{"localized_name":"file_path","name":"file_path","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"file_path"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"dictionary_name","name":"dictionary_name","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"dictionary_name"},"link":null